s a place here for ye, wandering around Norrath and looking, fate brought ye here and now I am happy to see that ye finally heard that call. Now there could be some that feel they were brought here, but in the same breath I talk to them as well, for we don’t want ye time here to have a bad taste in the mouth after meeting us. So we shall figure it out together ye and I, to see what best fits.<br><br>Although ye may not see a lot of the usual, “What we are” and “What we stand for” here in the Castle, I would like to say that there is a good reason for this. Here in the universe of the Avatar of Tunare Firiona Vie, ye may have seen something unlike any other place. So what are the reasons? Let the Battlemagus tell ye…<br><br>One reason above all things is that we are wrapped in the same origins for the most part. Yes, more elves then anything and sometimes we bicker and quarrel for that’s what brother and sister does. This is because every element of what ye must be, what ye must stand for, comes out here. Being true to yerself &lt;role-playing&gt; is the core of what we are. Trust me, as time goes on we shall discover ye and all the quarks that come with that package. Also if ye have problems developing a “persona,” we have some of the best in the universe right here. <br><br>Also, if ye think that the best thing to do is pillage and plunder and serve ye own needs, then this place is not for ye. We were in the bowls of Befallen for days at the edge of no sleep no food and no water, in recovery of each other, because we respect each other. So if ye don’t want to cater to that thing we call “respect” ye may not want to wander inside of the halls of the Court. This is a great reason that the Court is strong; because we know that the individual is important, just as the whole. However please remember that we have some old personas, and being an elder, I will be a bit headstrong in the things I say, but I think that for the most part, we are all fair. Respect the Court, and the way we communicate via the “Castle Halls.” &lt;Guild-chat&gt;<br><br>Now the rest is well a bit up to ye. Seek us out! Its the best way that we know what ye heart is. My brothers and sisters are of many different seasons, and usually on the best behavior. Simply tell them that the Battlemagus sent ye, and I shall confirm it. Then we can see what ye are right from the eyes of the court. <br><br>Now, right before ye run out there and get started, know that the journey that we take here does not run right into instant satisfaction. We all work hard and do a quest more then anything. There is no, coughs oh me Tunare, don’t burn me tongue…”lewt doodz” here. This is a realm of fantasy, and we are fantastic creatures. This realm is not the same as where ye came from, we don’t allow the Castle halls to be flooded with useless banter. Above and beyond all things, be true. That all ye need for others to know what lies within, and the seat in the court to shine there for ye. <br><br>Now I have said enough. Ye need my assistance call on me in the realm. I can perhaps get ye together with one of my brothers and sisters around ye season, and even give ye a magical weapon, from the summoner’s realm, the Maelstrom. It lasts until ye sleep so don’t go thinking that I got something like a…hell I don’t know I use a staff! Take care and Au’Bach! Means love forever…<br><br>Oh! In addition I almost forgot…<br><br>Read about us and understand the tales. Then ye shall know more about how fantastic of creatures we are. Take care for now…<br> <p><img src="http://baptiser.50megs.com/images/serion_aubauch.jpg" border="0"></a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/utivonaaubauch.showPublicProfile?language=EN> Tivona AuBauch</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.elchtom.de/Fantasy/f8.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member of the Court</span><br>  Posts: 14